DESCRIPTION:Every Thursday from 5-6PM\n(From 1/1/26 to 12/3/26) \nAt Lotus Education and Arts Foundation\n105 S. Rogers Street\nBloomington\, IN \nDetails\nInterested in art? Want to improve your art skills\, practice and experiment with new styles? Join us every Thursday from 5-6PM. For questions\, please email nogagordon@gmail.com.
